name: Bouncing Frame18
description:
My contribution to the BouncingOBJKT24 collaboration run by @jeremy_pires.

'#bouncingOBJKT24 is a small testimony of the amazing nft community that HEN has built and made possible. A Bouncing OBJKT made of 24 frames from 24 HEN artists all gathered in 1 loop. Thanks to all those kind and talented people, we are the #24for24'
